race.comment: Open race to close out the card. FLYING AURELIUS (5) resumes here but has won first-up before and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Best figures should see him run well. ESJAY (4) was a dominant five length winner at the latest Ipswich outing and will take a bunch of confidence from that victory. Has the talent to test this line-up. HEYOKA (11) is usually thereabouts and is one for the multiples. ECLAIR AWESOME (7) returned with a bang on the Sunshine Coast a couple of weeks ago and will relish getting her two into the ground. She looks a progressive mare on the rise and with that run under her belt, there's no reason why she can't go on with the job.
